: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">入驻开店条件（公司性质的合作对象）</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">① 注册资金500万元人民币以上。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">② 成立年限须满足一年以上。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">相关材料</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">① 公司介绍材料。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">② 五个以上行业相关成交案例。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">③ 营销推广渠道介绍。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">拍卖公司或营业范围中包含&ldquo;拍卖&rdquo;的非拍卖公司，需提供拍卖经营批准证书。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 63.8pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"85\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">司法拍卖</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 70.9pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: transparent; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"95\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">林权，土地，股权，住宅用房，机械设备，债权，其他财产，机动车，船舶，工程，工业用房，无形资产，商业用房，其他交通运输工具，其他用房，矿权</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 49.6pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 14.5pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"66\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width: 233.9pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: transparent; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 14.5pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"312\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">定向经营类目，在新增经营类目